# ISC2 CC Exam 考试介绍
考试形式：2hr 100道选择题 一道接一道不能回溯不能审查 700/1000 及格

## 如何准备：

https://www.isc2.org/Insights/2023/10/Fast-Track-Your-Career-Get-Certified-in-Cybersecurity-in-30-Days

Free online training 比实际考试简单 https://www.isc2.org/certifications/cc

